long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TopMoviesLinks Default Search is a premium search extension that provides an exceptional custom search experience powered by Bing, by configuring your Default Search to TopMoviesLinks Search.

Please read this part carefully:
By installing This Extension you agree to install this application, you agree to change your default search to TopMoviesLinks Search, and you agree to the End User License Agreement and the Privacy Policy.

More Information:
Start by typing preferred search term into the Google Chrome Omnibox. The TopMoviesLinks Search will provide excellent search results powered by Bing. User-friendly design and convenience in use guarantee you high level experience.
For more technical details you can read about Google Chrome API for Google Chrome Extensions.

You may remove this extension at any time from the chrome extension page.
Visit our website at https://topmovieslinks.com/
Read more about us at https://topmovieslinks.com/about/
